column5: I just noticed this came out yesterday, so for those looking, here you go. http://www.mnr.gov.on.ca/en/business/LetsFish/Publication/STEL02_163615.html
Cool thanks. Looks like no changes for Nipissing. 50 perch limit!...no problem!
Thanks Geoff! book marked for this new year.
I picked up a hardcopy today. Get them while you can....or if you can!  S.
Careful Chad, Nipissing regs are 25 Perch per day with a possession limit of 50.
says 50, no other perch regs. Me likey.
Careful Chad, Nipissing regs are 25 Perch per day with a possession limit of 50. Checked both Z11 regs and special extra's makes no such mention  S50.
Here is a highlight package for the changes in the regs.http://www.mnr.gov.on.ca/stdprodconsume/groups/lr/@mnr/@letsfish/documents/factsheet/stdprod_101636.pdf
